        <td id="descriptionArea">
            <p>Environment:</p>

<p>OS : Windows 11</p>

<p>Browser : Chrome</p>

<p>Steps to Reproduce:</p>

<ol>
	<li>Login to POSTMAN tool</li>
	<li>In POSTMAN tool, Navigate to My workspace-<del>&gt;Collection</del>&gt;Click Add new request</li>
	<li>Enter the URL <a href="https://restful-booker.herokuapp.com/booking" class="external-link" rel="nofollow noreferrer">https://restful-booker.herokuapp.com/booking</a> and Select Post request providing "totalprice"=-1.</li>
	<li>Verify if you  are getting status code of 400 error</li>
</ol>


<p>Expected Result:</p>

<p>The Booking should not be created with status code 400 Bad Request</p>

<p>Actual Result:</p>

<p>The booking is created</p>
